  <h1>
   ds_grid_get_disk_sum
  </h1>
  This function can be used to add all the values all the cells found within the defined disk area of a grid together, as shown in the image below:
  <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/GML/Reference/Data_Structures/ds_grid_get_disk_sum.png"/><br/>
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">ds_grid_get_disk_sum(index, xm, ym, r);
</code></pre>
  <table>
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <th>
      Argument
     </th>
     <th>
      Type
     </th>
     <th>
      Description
     </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      index
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       <a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Data_Structures/DS_Grids/ds_grid_create.htm">
        DS Grid ID
       </a>
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      The index of the grid.
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      xm
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       <a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Data_Types.htm">
        Real
       </a>
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      The x position of the disk on the grid.
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      ym
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       <a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Data_Types.htm">
        Real
       </a>
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      The y position of the disk on the grid.
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      r
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       <a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Data_Types.htm">
        Real
       </a>
      </span>
     </td>
     <td>
      The radius of the disk on the grid.
     </td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml"><a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Data_Types.htm">
 Real
</a>
or
<a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Data_Types.htm">
 String
</a></code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">val = ds_grid_get_disk_sum(grid, 5, 5, 2)
</code></pre>
  The above code will set the variable "val" to the sum of all values contained within the given disk of the DS grid indexed in the variable "grid".
 </body>
</html>